Welcome to Ramdeobaba University (RBU), where innovation meets
              tradition, and excellence is a way of life. Established with a
              vision to nurture talent, foster creativity, and promote
              holistic development, RBU stands as a beacon of quality
              education in India. With a rich history dating back to its
              inception, the university has continually evolved to meet the
              ever-changing needs of the educational landscape while
              upholding its core values of integrity, excellence, and
              inclusivity.
Job Opportunities
Engineering category - Rank Band 151-200

Innovation and technology converge to provide a world-class
                  learning environment. Our modern facilities include
                  well-equipped laboratories, spacious classrooms, libraries,
                  sports facilities, andcomfortable hostels. With a commitment
                  to providing an unparalleled educational experience, RCOEM has
                  invested in cutting-edge infrastructure that empowers students
                  to achieve their full potential.

We take great pride in our highly qualified faculty members
                  who bring a wealth of academic and industry experience to the
                  classroom. Our faculty members are experts in their respective
                  fields and are committed to providing students with the
                  knowledge and skills they need to succeed in their
                  careers.With a student-centered approach to teaching and
                  learning, our faculty members use innovative methods to engage
                  and inspire students, helping them reach their full potential
                  and achieve their academic and professional goals.

content.h3: Collaboration With Reputed Universities and Industries

content.p:
We have established collaborations with renowned universities
                  and industries to enhance its academic and research offerings.
                  Through these partnerships, RBU aims to provide its students
                  with cutting-edge technologies and industry exposure,
                  preparing them for the dynamic job market. These
                  collaborations also facilitate joint research projects,
                  exchange programs, and guest lectures by industry experts,
                  thereby fostering a culture of innovation and collaboration.

We have established a strong placement record over the years,
                  with leading companies across various industries visiting the
                  campus for recruitment. The institute's dedicated placement
                  cell prepares students for placements through training
                  programs, mock interviews, and industry interactions. RBU
                  graduates have secured placements with top-tier organizations
                  in India, showcasing the institute's commitment to excellence
                  in education and industry engagement. The strong placement
                  record is a testament to RCOEM's reputation as one of the best
                  private engineering colleges in India for higher education and
                  career growth

Ramdeobaba University (RBU) stands as a testament to a
                forty-year educational journey, rooted in the cultivation of
                human potential with a strong emphasis on universal values.
                Formerly known as Shri Ramdeobaba College of Engineering and
                Management (RCOEM), the university inherits a rich legacy from
                its predecessor.

Established in 1984 by the Shri Ramdeobaba Sarvajanik Samiti,
                Nagpur, under the visionary leadership of founding chairman Shri
                Banwarilal Purohit, currently serving as the Honourable Governor
                of Punjab and Administrator of Chandigarh, RCOEM saw a
                transformative era under the stewardship of Shri Satyanarayan
                Nuwal, CEO of Solar Group of Industries, recognized among
                India's top 100 CEOs. This leadership propelled RCOEM to
